This folder estimates cell type proportions using CIBERSORTx. First, use the script ScriptPriorToCIBERSORTx.Rmd. Then run CIBERSORTx online at https://cibersortx.stanford.edu/  .
Then use the script ScriptAfterCIBERSORTx.Rmd.

CIBERSORTx_Results.csv is the raw results file we obtained for our data using the CIBERSORTx website. 
